### 1. Register a New User
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

###

### 2. Login to get Access Token
# @name loginRequest
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Capture the token from the response
@authToken = {{loginRequest.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
@refreshToken = {{loginRequest.response.body.$.data.tokens.refreshToken}}

###

### 3. Get Monthly Report
GET http://localhost:4000/api/reports/monthly/2025/12
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 4. Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### 5. Create a Transaction
POST http://localhost:4000/api/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "category": "Salary",
  "description": "December Paycheck",
  "date": "2025-01-15T00:00:00.000Z",
  "type": "INCOME"
}
